<i>Tell me something good</i>

01:31.294 --> 01:33.023
<i>Only you</i>

01:33.196 --> 01:35.096
<i>But how can you know for sure?</i>

01:35.265 --> 01:38.200
<i>Can make this world seem right</i>

01:38.368 --> 01:39.926
