<i>Don't have to be rich to be my girl</i>

03:20.738 --> 03:25.732
<i>Don't have to be cool to rule my world</i>

03:25.910 --> 03:27.400
<i>You rule my world</i>

03:27.578 --> 03:32.277
<i>You're the particular song</i>
<i>I'm compatible with</i>

03:32.449 --> 03:34.280
<i>I just want your</i>

